	    <p id="copyright">Â© 2009. All Rights Reserved. <br/>
	      Designed and Programmed by WUS Team</a> from <u><a href="http://www.pace.edu" target="_blank">Pace University</a></u>.</p>
	  </div>
	  <!-- /footer -->
	</body>
</html>